the adventure ahead!

1172
01:31:16,620 --> 01:31:18,554
Doctor...

1173
01:31:20,758 --> 01:31:26,196
you mentioned the ratio
of ten women to each man.

1174
01:31:26,264 --> 01:31:29,393
Now, wouldn't that
necessitate the abandonment...

1175
01:31:29,468 --> 01:31:33,268
of the so-called
monogamous sexual relationship?

1176
01:31:33,338 --> 01:31:36,968
I mean, as far as men were concerned?

1177
01:31:37,043 --> 01:31:38,408
Regrettably, yes.

1178
01:31:38,478 --> 01:31:43,849
But it is a sacrifice required
for the future of the human race.

1179
01:31:43,918 --> 01:31:48,913
I hasten to add that since each man
will be required to do prodigious...

1180
01:31:50,692 --> 01:31:52,626
service along these lines...

1181
01:31:52,694 --> 01:31:56,495
the women will have to be selected
for their sexual characteristics...

1182
01:31:56,566 --> 01:32:00,332
which will have to be of
a highly stimulating nature.

1183
01:32:00,403 --> 01:32:04,238
I must confess, you have an
astonishingly good idea there, Doctor.

1184
01:32:05,409 --> 01:32:06,842
Thank you, sir.

1185
01:32:06,910 --> 01:32:09,880
We ought to look at this
from the military point of view.

1186
01:32:09,948 --> 01:32:13,884
I mean,
supposing the Ruskies...

1187
01:32:13,952 --> 01:32:16,887
stashed away some big bombs,
see, and we didn't?

1188
01:32:16,955 --> 01:32:19,857
When they come out in 100 years,
they could take over!

1189
01:32:19,925 --> 01:32:21,688
I agree, Mr. President.

1190
01:32:21,760 --> 01:32:25,356
They might try a sneak attack so they
could take over our mine shaft space.

1191
01:32:25,432 --> 01:32:30,062
It'd be extremely naive of us to
imagine that these new developments...

1192
01:32:30,136 --> 01:32:33,072
are gonna cause any change
in Soviet expansionist policy!

1193
01:32:33,140 --> 01:32:35,973
I mean, we must be
increasingly on the alert...

1194
01:32:36,043 --> 01:32:38,569
to prevent them from taking over
other mine shaft space...

1195
01:32:38,647 --> 01:32:40,581
in order to breed more
prodigiously than we do...

1196
01:32:40,649 --> 01:32:43,777
thus knocking us out through
superior numbers when we emerge!

1197
01:32:43,852 --> 01:32:47,949
Mr. President, we must not allow
a mine-shaft gap!

1198
01:32:48,024 --> 01:32:50,117
Sir!

1199
01:32:50,193 --> 01:32:52,457
I have a plan...

1200
01:32:53,998 --> 01:32:56,330
<i>Mein Fuhrer...</i>

1201
01:32:56,400 --> 01:32:58,994
I can walk!

